def get_highest_priced_item(shop: OnlineShop):     stock = shop.get_stock()     items = stock.get_items()      if not items:         return None  # Return None if there are no items in the stock.      highest_priced_item = max(items, key=lambda item: item.get_price())     return highest_priced_item
